snippet.title: WitchGhost Trailer
snippet.description:
🎮 First Trailer for WitchGhost - My Debut Video Game! 🎮

Dive into the enchanting world of WitchGhost, a charming and spooky exploration game! Join Ezme, the WitchGhost, on her quest to recover her lost memories and find her way back home.

✨ Features:

Explore eerie and atmospheric landscapes
Battle spooky enemies
Dodge tricky traps
Cast a variety of unique and magical spells

🕹️ Demo Available Now! 

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2711050/WitchGhost/
Itch.io: https://personalerror.itch.io/witchghost
